1. Put enc.sh and dec.sh to home folder ~ (or other folder what you want).

2. Create your key at ~/Desktop/.key
   Just vim the key file and type what you want to be the key.

3. Encrypt/Decrypt a file/folder:
   ~/enc.sh file/folder
   ~/dec.sh file.des3

4. Encrypt/Decrypt all files under a folder.
   ~/enc.sh
   ~/dec.sh
